## ğŸ§  Design & Architecture Decisions

- Pygame was chosen for rapid prototyping and full control over game mechanics
- The mask system is modular, allowing easy expansion
- Every power includes a meaningful disability to enforce balance
- Visual simplicity was prioritized to focus on gameplay depth

Smart trade-offs were made to deliver a complete and playable prototype within hackathon time constraints.

